      <title>汽油价格上涨对低收入美国人的打击最大</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/06/business/economy/gas-prices-inequality-lower-income-consumers.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着汽油价格飙升，收入较低的人开车的次数越来越少，并将更多的预算投入到交通运输上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/06/business/economy/gas-prices-inequality-lower-income-consumers.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 16:07:51 GMT</pubDate>
